\end_inset

 is of the following piece-wise form
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
F(x) & =\begin{cases}
A & 0<x<\mu\\
B & \mu<x<1-\mu\\
C & 1-\mu<x<1\\
0 & \text{otherwise}
\end{cases}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


